      "widgets": [
        {
          "id": "content-markdown",
          "kind": "builtin:markdown",
          "title": "What does Boardstate HQ track?",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 0, "w": 12, "h": 6 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "markdown": "# What does Boardstate HQ track?\n\n**agent:growth** · answered 2h ago · sourced from `usage.cost` + `sessions.list`\n\nBoardstate HQ is a single JSON workspace document that fans every builtin widget kind across four tabs — **Data**, **Operations**, **Content**, and **Embeds**. Every binding on this template is `static`, so the whole thing renders identically with no live backend wired up.\n\n| Tab | Purpose |\n| --- | --- |\n| Data | Stat cards, a table, and every chart type (area/bar/line/gauge) |\n| Operations | Sessions, usage, cron, instances, agent status, activity, approvals |\n| Content | Markdown, notes, and the action-form prompt pattern |\n| Embeds | A sandboxed preview frame and a raw iframe embed |\n\nSwap any `static` binding for an `rpc`, `file`, or `stream` source to wire it to real data — the widget renderers don't change."
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "content-ask",
          "kind": "builtin:action-form",
          "title": "Ask the Agent",
          "grid": { "x": 0, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "template": "Draft a {tone} summary about {topic}.",
            "fields": [
              { "name": "topic", "label": "Topic", "type": "text", "maxLength": 80 },
              {
                "name": "tone",
                "label": "Tone",
                "type": "select",
                "options": ["concise", "friendly", "formal"]
              }
            ],
            "buttonLabel": "Ask the agent"
          }
        },
        {
          "id": "content-notes",
          "kind": "builtin:notes",
          "title": "Scratchpad",
          "grid": { "x": 6, "y": 6, "w": 6, "h": 6 },
          "collapsed": false,
          "hidden": false,
          "props": {
            "text": "Starter note — this pad is agent- and human-editable and persists via write-back state. Jot follow-ups from the Data and Operations tabs here."
          }
        }
      ]
